In re BRUEN et al. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. February 4, 1903.) No. 101. Petition for Revision of Proceedings of the District Court of the United States for the Southern District of New York. Ralph E. Paine, for petitioner. Waldo G. Morse, for respondent.

Before LACOMBE, TOWNSEND, and COXE, Circuit Judges.

Upon filing stipulation, appeal is dis-missed.
